Sharks. I think that buy now everybody and their uncle knows about sharks because of the blockbuster movie that gives EVERYONE nightmares: Jaws. But do not let that stop you from getting this game. Because at first it stopped me. Then thanks to Youtube and the popular user PhoneInk, Its now one of my personal favorites! :D For Gluten's first entirely underwater game, its pretty good! The underwater world is absoulutely breathtaking, and the whole "beneath the waves" thing is very intriguing and executed perfectly by the company. The seven different sharks add a great aspect to the game, and all the different skin colors and patterns, (five for each type of shark to be exact), are totally awesome and very fun to unlock at the different stages/levels. I hope that this review helps Gluten with the sales of this amazing app. :)
